<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.3">
<l>ceppōtu meṉmulai yārkaḷ ciṟucōṟu millum citaittiṭṭu</l>
<l>appōtu nāṉurap pappō yaṭicilu muṇṭilai yāḷvāy</l>
<l>muppōtum vāṉava rēttum muṉivarkaḷ veḷḷaṟai niṉṟā</l>
<l>yippōtu nāṉoṉṟum ceyyē ṉempirāṉ kāppiṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Supreme Lord! When, having destroyed the little [toy] rice [dishes]</l>
<l rend="indent">and [sand] houses of the [girls] with soft copper pot-like breast,</l>
<l rend="indent">I became angry [and] you wouldn’t eat any food!</l>
<l>You who stands in Veḷḷaṟai with sages</l>
<l rend="indent">who praise the gods three times [daily],</l>
<l>My Lord, I won’t do anything this time.</l>
<l rend="indent">Come so that [I can] fasten a kāppu!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
